Dmg-Song is so much underrated! If you hit for 200 dmg and 40 are added by our song - that's 20% more dmg! People are spending tons of platinum for MP weapons which will give them much less bang for the bucks. 3 melee fighter in your group-&gt;120 dmg per hit, which means roughly a fourth 1 hand melee.<br>
